Data licensing
==============

This repository contains source code only. Derived data products
(featurized ICSD embeddings, community assignments, per-source frontier
record CSVs, summary JSONs, etc.) are deposited separately on Zenodo
under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0)
license; see README.md for the Zenodo DOI.

ICSD itself is licensed by FIZ Karlsruhe (https://icsd.products.fiz-
karlsruhe.de). Users who wish to regenerate the embeddings from the raw
ICSD CIF source must obtain their own ICSD license; this repository
does not redistribute ICSD CIFs.
